body.name: Air Wick Freshmatic Air Freshener Spray Starter Kit (1 Gadget + 1 Refill) Automatic Sprayer, Sparkling Peach and Apricot Scent for Home and Office Fragrance
body.stockDetail: Only 4 left in stock - order soon.
features: FRAGRANCE: Bring the delights of summer into your home with this playful and fun fragrance including fresh juicy fruits
UP TO 70 DAYS OF FRESHNESS: Each refill provides up to 70 days on low setting of automatic and continuous fragrance. Replace refill can when there is a red flashing light
USE IN ANY ROOM: living room, bathroom, hallways, kitchens, den and office

Fill your home with the scent of fresh juicy fruits with this AIR WICK FRESHMATIC KIT SPARKLING PEACH AND APRICOT The fragrance with natural essential oils keeps your home smelling fresh day after day for up to 70 days. The kit includes a device, refill and battery.

AIR WICK FRESHMATIC AUTOSPRAY SPARKLING PEACH AND APRICOT automatically releases bursts of continuous fragrance to constantly freshen your home and neutralise odours. One spritz is enough to fill a room, and make your home always smells welcoming. Just set the air freshener to your preferred fragrance intensity setting and enjoy the great smell.
body.description: Air Wick Automatic Air Freshener spray fills your home with continuous, fresh fragrance. The latest Freshmatic diffuser provides up to 70 days of freshness per refill on the 40 minutes setting. The sprays bursts at 9, 18 or 40 minutes settings to achieve desired fragrance level. Enjoy the continuous freshness in your bathroom, living room, office or den. Get the confidence of knowing that your home is always welcoming and pleasurable for family and unexpected guests.
